  <brief_title>Safety and Tolerability of SPD485 in Children Aged 6-12 Diagnosed With ADHD and Previously Participated in MTS Trials</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Multi-center, Open-label Study of Methylphenidate Transdermal System (MTS) in Pediatric Patients Aged 6-12 With Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)</official_title>
