  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the long-term safety of MTS in the symptomatic treatment of children
      aged 6-12 diagnosed with ADHD
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) is a psychiatric disorder characterized by 3
      main symptoms: inattention, hyperactivity and impulsivity. This study will evaluate the
      long-term safety of SPD485 in the symptomatic treatment of children aged 6-12 diagnosed with
      ADHD
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
